        <a href="http://people.ubuntu.com/~ubuntu-security/cve/CVE-2014-3509">CVE-2014-3509</a>, 

        <a href="http://people.ubuntu.com/~ubuntu-security/cve/CVE-2014-3510">CVE-2014-3510</a>, 

        <a href="http://people.ubuntu.com/~ubuntu-security/cve/CVE-2014-3511">CVE-2014-3511</a>, 

        <a href="http://people.ubuntu.com/~ubuntu-security/cve/CVE-2014-3512">CVE-2014-3512</a>, 

        <a href="http://people.ubuntu.com/~ubuntu-security/cve/CVE-2014-5139">CVE-2014-5139</a>
        

</p>





